	"description" : "Every day, we come across countless forms and landscapes of everyday life.
No matter how new the appearance of daily life and the thrilling landscapes are seen, when you face them every day, you can easily pass by.
Sometimes I feel dry emotions.
Daymood is an artwork created to keep the appearances of such scenery a little bit different and new.
By expressing everyday landscapes in colorful colors according to the feelings of the artist, people who see the artwork can also express various emotions in their daily lives.
It is inducing you to feel.

5184 x 3456px / 300dpi / 22.2mb",
